bugs that have a demonstrable security impact on smart contracts are in' 'scope For example a Solidity program whose optimization is incorrect eg' 'leads to an incorrect output qualifies as a security bug Please note that the' 'rules of the Ethereum bounty program have precedence over this security policy' 'SSuuppppoorrtteedd VVeerrssiioonnss' 'As a general rule only the latest release gets affects' 'Example  Assuming the current release is  and a security bug has been' 'found in it that affects both x and x trees we may not only patch' ' the bugfix release numbered  but x as well the
